        Selling a Property With a Granny Flat in Brisbane: Valuation, Marketing and Buyer Appeal
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        Granny flats attract a specific buyer profile, are valued differently to standard homes, and come with marketing rules that sellers need to understand before listing.
      </p>
    </div>
